  "remarks": "FSE Aleksin Chemical Plant is a Russian enterprise that produces a range of industrial chemicals used in the manufacture of gunpowder and weapons charges. FSE Aleksin Chemical Plant supplies state-owned plants that produce gunpowder, cartridges and ammunition for the Russian Armed Forces. FSE Aleksin Chemical Plant is a major producer and supplier of chemical materials of strategic importance to the Russian defence sector.",
